00:23:12,630 --> 00:23:13,540
bumalik sa trono.

252
00:23:15,500 --> 00:23:17,020
Anumang balita sa Left Token?

253
00:23:17,740 --> 00:23:18,740
Hindi pa nahanap.

254
00:23:21,190 --> 00:23:23,580
Paano naman sina Jiang Ai at Bai Sanxing?

255
00:23:24,100 --> 00:23:24,940
Naghahanap pa.

256
00:23:25,780 --> 00:23:26,670
Limang taon na.

257
00:23:27,190 --> 00:23:28,780
Hindi ka pa nakakahanap ng dalawang espiritu!

258
00:23:30,820 --> 00:23:31,660
Ang iyong Panginoon,

259
00:23:31,950 --> 00:23:32,820
basta Jiang Ai

260
00:23:32,820 --> 00:23:33,780
hawak pa rin ang Token,

261
00:23:34,430 --> 00:23:35,300
hindi namin mabuksan

262
00:23:35,300 --> 00:23:36,430
ang imbakan ng batong espiritu

263
00:23:36,870 --> 00:23:37,910
upang maalis ang anumang mga bato.

264
00:23:38,870 --> 00:23:40,230
Limang taon na siyang nagtatago.

265
00:23:40,740 --> 00:23:41,580
Ang aming mga espiritung bato

266
00:23:41,820 --> 00:23:42,870
halos maubos na.

267
00:23:43,500 --> 00:23:44,340
At kahapon,

268
00:23:44,340 --> 00:23:45,710
isang malaking bilang ng mga espiritu ang natipon.

269
00:23:46,190 --> 00:23:47,300
Inatake nila ang 24 na Templo

270
00:23:47,300 --> 00:23:48,140
at hinalughog sila.

271
00:23:49,260 --> 00:23:50,100
Sa kabutihang palad, pinangunahan ko ang aking mga tauhan

272
00:23:50,670 --> 00:23:51,510
upang ipatupad ang mga ito.

273
00:23:53,470 --> 00:23:54,670
Sa labas ng Sovereign's Hall,

274
00:23:54,990 --> 00:23:56,190
nagkaroon ng kaguluhan sa lahat ng dako.

275
00:23:56,820 --> 00:23:57,660
tama yan.

276
00:24:15,740 --> 00:24:16,580
Ang iyong Panginoon,

277
00:24:16,780 --> 00:24:17,780
nahanap namin si Jiang Ai.

278
00:24:26,740 --> 00:24:28,980
(Ascension Pool)

279
00:24:40,580 --> 00:24:41,430
Yan Ke,

280
00:24:42,390 --> 00:24:43,540
dahil nandito ka,

281
00:24:44,100 --> 00:24:45,390
bakit hindi ka lumabas?

282
00:24:49,950 --> 00:24:51,150
Bigyan mo ako ng Left Token

283
00:24:51,740 --> 00:24:53,500
at hahayaan kitang umalis sa Void.

284
00:24:55,100 --> 00:24:56,820
Ayokong hinahabol ako

285
00:24:57,190 --> 00:24:59,340
ng Starhaven Sect
sa Mortal World.

286
00:24:59,740 --> 00:25:00,820
Pagkatapos ay manatili ka dito

287
00:25:00,820 --> 00:25:01,950
at mapuksa!

288
00:25:17,150 --> 00:25:17,990
Yan Ke,

289
00:25:18,500 --> 00:25:19,910
how dare you appear before me?

290
00:25:22,580 --> 00:25:24,430
Alam ba ni Simu na inilabas mo

291
00:25:25,820 --> 00:25:26,870
ang dati mong manliligaw?

292
00:25:27,820 --> 00:25:29,670
Hayaan mong tanungin kita nito.

293
00:25:30,500 --> 00:25:32,780
Kung malalaman ni Simu

294
00:25:32,780 --> 00:25:34,670
pinatay mo ang kanyang ama,

295
00:25:35,340 --> 00:25:36,820
ano gagawin mo

296
00:25:39,390 --> 00:25:40,230
Ano...

297
00:25:52,670 --> 00:25:54,580
Pinatay mo pa ang sarili mong uri.

298
00:25:55,100 --> 00:25:56,430
Wala ka talagang awa.

299
00:25:57,540 --> 00:25:58,580
Ikaw noon

300
00:25:58,580 --> 00:26:00,150
na pumatay sa ama ni He Simu.

301
00:26:00,580 --> 00:26:02,630
Pero nanatili ka sa tabi niya nang mapanlinlang

302
00:26:03,020 --> 00:26:04,060
at hiniling sa kanya na patayin ako,

303
00:26:04,060 --> 00:26:05,300
ang tanging saksi sa katotohanan.

304
00:26:05,710 --> 00:26:07,150
Kung malalaman ni He Simu,

305
00:26:09,670 --> 00:26:11,300
hihiwalayan ka niya.

306
00:26:12,780 --> 00:26:14,910
Kaya pala kinakabahan ka.

307
00:26:15,670 --> 00:26:16,540
Kaya hindi ka natakot

308
00:26:16,540 --> 00:26:18,150
na hahanapin ka ni Bai Sanxing.

309
00:26:18,710 --> 00:26:20,150
Natakot ka

310
00:26:20,150 --> 00:26:21,870
na malalaman ng Her Grace ang totoo

311
00:26:22,020 --> 00:26:23,870
pagkatapos niyang makipagkita kay Bai Sanxing.

312
00:26:24,260 --> 00:26:25,990
Masyado kang nagsasalita.

313
00:26:33,580 --> 00:26:34,740
300 taon na ang nakalipas,

314
00:26:34,740 --> 00:26:36,190
Baka natakot ako sayo.

315
00:26:36,630 --> 00:26:37,580
Ngunit na-stuck doon

316
00:26:37,580 --> 00:26:38,710
sa mahabang panahon

317
00:26:39,260 --> 00:26:40,910
ay iniwan kang mas mahina kaysa dati.

318
00:27:02,670 --> 00:27:03,510
umalis.

319
00:27:10,380 --> 00:27:12,700
(Kaliwa)

320
00:27:16,260 --> 00:27:17,950
Hindi ka makakawala.

321
00:27:19,300 --> 00:27:20,820
Ang buong Void

322
00:27:21,670 --> 00:27:24,060
malapit nang maging akin.

323
00:27:59,260 --> 00:28:00,100
Simu,

324
00:28:01,100 --> 00:28:02,300
Naalala ko bigla.

325
00:28:02,990 --> 00:28:03,870
Ngayon ang araw

326
00:28:03,870 --> 00:28:05,230
una tayong nagkita 300 years ago.

327
00:28:05,950 --> 00:28:07,500
Dapat nating ipagdiwang ang anibersaryo na ito.

328
00:28:11,430 --> 00:28:12,500
Noong araw na iyon, sa pagkakaalala ko,

329
00:28:12,990 --> 00:28:14,300
libu-libong espiritu ang naghimagsik.

330
00:28:14,820 --> 00:28:16,060
Hawak mo ang Kunwu Blade

331
00:28:16,430 --> 00:28:18,260
upang sugpuin sila nang mag-isa.

332
00:28:19,630 --> 00:28:21,060
Iyon ang unang pagkakataon na nakita kita.

333
00:28:22,260 --> 00:28:23,740
Nagniningning ka nang husto.

334
00:28:25,230 --> 00:28:26,070
Simu,

335
00:28:27,100 --> 00:28:28,230
lagi mong sinasabi

336
00:28:28,230 --> 00:28:29,820
Gusto ko ng pinakamataas na kapangyarihan.

337
00:28:30,910 --> 00:28:31,750
Mali ka.

338
00:28:32,390 --> 00:28:33,470
Gusto ko pareho,

339
00:28:34,630 --> 00:28:35,470
ikaw at kapangyarihan.

340
00:28:37,580 --> 00:28:39,340
Kung wala ka, hindi ko kaya

341
00:28:39,340 --> 00:28:40,430
pamahalaan ang Void ng maayos.

342
00:28:40,910 --> 00:28:41,750
Kung wala ka,

343
00:28:43,950 --> 00:28:45,710
lahat ay magiging walang kabuluhan.

344
00:28:57,670 --> 00:28:58,670
Ngayon ay talagang isang araw

345
00:28:58,670 --> 00:28:59,990
sulit na ipagdiwang.

346
00:29:01,440 --> 00:29:02,300
300 taon na ang nakalipas,

347
00:29:02,300 --> 00:29:03,670
biglang namatay ang tatay ko.

348
00:29:05,190 --> 00:29:06,150
Wala akong choice

349
00:29:07,260 --> 00:29:08,500
ngunit upang sakupin ang Void.

350
00:29:15,870 --> 00:29:16,820
At ngayon,

351
00:29:19,740 --> 00:29:21,580
Papatayin ko yung isa
na pumatay sa aking ama.

352
00:29:39,340 --> 00:29:41,950
Ikaw... Alam mo yun?

353
00:29:44,260 --> 00:29:46,060
Narinig ko ang sinabi mo

354
00:29:46,950 --> 00:29:48,340
sa Void Mountain.

355
00:30:08,100 --> 00:30:09,630
Marami akong nagawa nitong mga taon.

356
00:30:09,630 --> 00:30:11,060
Ito ang tanging bagay

357
00:30:11,870 --> 00:30:13,300
Hindi ko gustong malaman mo.

358
00:30:14,950 --> 00:30:16,820
Noon, gusto kong maging Soberano.

359
00:30:16,820 --> 00:30:18,190
Kaya wala akong choice

360
00:30:18,190 --> 00:30:19,740
ngunit upang patayin siya.

361
00:30:21,260 --> 00:30:22,500
Ngunit para sa iyong kapakanan,

362
00:30:23,300 --> 00:30:24,300
Ako ang naging Kanang Kamay

363
00:30:24,300 --> 00:30:25,580
sa nakalipas na 300 taon

364
00:30:25,580 --> 00:30:27,020
at hindi nagreklamo!

365
00:30:29,190 --> 00:30:31,150
Pero hindi mo pa rin ako tanggap.

366
00:30:32,500 --> 00:30:34,580
Kaya kailangan kitang ikulong dito.

367
00:30:39,300 --> 00:30:40,190
Ngunit lahat ng mga bagay na ito

368
00:30:40,190 --> 00:30:41,470
hindi na mahalaga.

369
00:30:42,540 --> 00:30:43,380
Simu,

370
00:30:44,500 --> 00:30:45,910
Babayaran kita.

371
00:30:47,300 --> 00:30:48,580
Gusto mo ang Mortal World, tama ba?

372
00:30:49,260 --> 00:30:51,100
I wouldn't mind uniting

373
00:30:51,100 --> 00:30:52,100
ang dalawang mundo.

374
00:30:52,820 --> 00:30:54,150
Kahit saan mo gustong pumunta,

375
00:30:54,430 --> 00:30:55,500
Pupunta ako diyan kasama mo.

376
00:30:57,060 --> 00:30:58,670
Wag mo lang akong iwan.

377
00:31:02,870 --> 00:31:04,020
Pinatay mo ang tatay ko.

378
00:31:07,880 --> 00:31:08,740
Ginagawa ba nito

379
00:31:08,740 --> 00:31:10,230
bagay na bagay talaga?

380
00:31:12,190 --> 00:31:13,740
Kung hindi ko siya pinatay,

381
00:31:14,500 --> 00:31:15,500
iba ba ang mga bagay

382
00:31:15,500 --> 00:31:16,780
sa pagitan natin?

383
00:31:18,820 --> 00:31:20,020
Walang kung!

384
00:31:49,260 --> 00:31:50,300
Dito ang tatay mo

385
00:31:50,300 --> 00:31:52,060
itinatag ang Golden-wall Decrees.

386
00:31:54,540 --> 00:31:56,100
Gusto mo siyang ipaghiganti, hindi ba?

387
00:31:57,670 --> 00:31:59,260
Tapos na natin ito

388
00:31:59,540 --> 00:32:00,630
dito at ngayon.

389
00:33:30,150 --> 00:33:30,990
Itigil ang pagtugis.

390
00:33:32,150 --> 00:33:33,230
Iyon ang aking oversight.

391
00:33:34,740 --> 00:33:36,100
Nagkunwari siyang inaaway ako

392
00:33:36,540 --> 00:33:37,740
para lang sunggaban ang Glazed Pagoda

393
00:33:38,260 --> 00:33:39,780
upang itago ang kanyang aura at gawin ang kanyang pagtakas.

394
00:33:40,990 --> 00:33:42,430
Out of reach na siya ngayon.

395
00:34:19,100 --> 00:34:20,430
Pinatalsik ka sa Void?

396
00:34:28,540 --> 00:34:29,540
Sino ang nagpapahintulot sa iyo

397
00:34:29,540 --> 00:34:31,060
para kausapin ako ng ganito?

398
00:34:33,620 --> 00:34:34,870
Pumunta ka dito

399
00:34:34,870 --> 00:34:36,020
para humingi ng tulong sa akin, hindi ba?

400
00:34:37,270 --> 00:34:38,110
Tulong?

401
00:34:39,100 --> 00:34:40,020
Hindi mo ito deserve.

402
00:34:41,270 --> 00:34:42,430
Kung ganoon,

403
00:34:43,310 --> 00:34:44,350
Hindi kita pipigilan.

404
00:34:48,700 --> 00:34:50,700
Isa ka lang nakasangla.

405
00:34:51,660 --> 00:34:52,950
Kaya kitang bigyan ng kapangyarihan,

406
00:34:53,270 --> 00:34:55,220
at maaari ko itong bawiin anumang oras.

407
00:34:56,140 --> 00:34:57,700
Mas mabuting ituwid mo iyon.

408
00:34:59,060 --> 00:35:00,750
Huwag isipin ang pagiging High Priest

409
00:35:01,100 --> 00:35:02,830
ibig sabihin wala kang dapat ipag-alala.

410
00:35:04,140 --> 00:35:06,180
Kung bumagsak ang North Chong,

411
00:35:06,700 --> 00:35:08,950
mapapahamak ka rin nito.

412
00:35:18,790 --> 00:35:20,700
Hindi kailanman natatalo si Duan Xu sa isang labanan

413
00:35:21,430 --> 00:35:23,750
dahil lang may kasunduan siya
kasama ang Soberano.

414
00:35:24,950 --> 00:35:26,470
Hindi nakakagulat sa Youzhou,

415
00:35:27,430 --> 00:35:29,790
ang kanyang kapangyarihan ay walang kaparis.

416
00:35:30,910 --> 00:35:31,750
tama yan.

417
00:35:34,310 --> 00:35:36,020
Ang Soberano ay bumalik sa trono.

418
00:35:36,910 --> 00:35:39,220
Maaapektuhan ang takbo ng digmaan.

419
00:35:43,220 --> 00:35:44,100
Ano ang dapat kong gawin?

420
00:35:46,660 --> 00:35:47,660
Kapag nasa paligid ako,

421
00:35:48,390 --> 00:35:49,950
magtatagumpay ka.

422
00:35:51,830 --> 00:35:54,470
Ang kailangan mo lang gawin ay sundin ang aking mga utos.

423
00:36:10,310 --> 00:36:11,270
Simu,

424
00:36:11,270 --> 00:36:12,430
sa wakas nakabalik ka na.

425
00:36:28,020 --> 00:36:28,860
Bai Sanxing,

426
00:36:30,790 --> 00:36:32,060
ano ang iyong mga plano para sa hinaharap?

427
00:36:33,430 --> 00:36:34,500
Ipaglalaban mo pa ba ako

428
00:36:34,500 --> 00:36:35,620
para sa trono?

429
00:36:39,390 --> 00:36:40,230
Ito ay depende.

430
00:36:40,910 --> 00:36:41,870
300 taon na ang nakalipas,

431
00:36:41,870 --> 00:36:42,910
Tumayo ako laban kay He Yicheng.

432
00:36:43,470 --> 00:36:44,350
Tapos ngayon,

433
00:36:46,180 --> 00:36:47,060
Kaya kong gawin ang parehong.

434
00:36:49,580 --> 00:36:50,420
Maghihintay ako.

435
00:36:51,220 --> 00:36:52,180
Huwag mag-atubiling subukan.

436
00:36:57,020 --> 00:36:57,860
Noon,

437
00:36:58,060 --> 00:36:59,500
Naniwala ako kay Yan Ke.

438
00:37:32,370 --> 00:37:33,220
Akala ko ibig niyang sabihin

439
00:37:33,220 --> 00:37:34,270
para tulungan ako,

440
00:37:34,500 --> 00:37:35,390
kaya pinatay niya si He Yicheng

441
00:37:35,950 --> 00:37:37,700
at nagkalat ng tsismis na namatay siya para sa pag-ibig.

442
00:37:38,990 --> 00:37:39,830
Nagulat ako,

443
00:37:40,180 --> 00:37:41,060
siya tapos

444
00:37:41,470 --> 00:37:43,020
nagtrabaho sa iyo upang bitag ako.

445
00:37:48,180 --> 00:37:49,580
Hanggang sa sila ni Jiang Ai

446
00:37:50,100 --> 00:37:51,350
dinala ako sa Bilangguan

447
00:37:51,660 --> 00:37:53,060
at inatake ako ng tatlo

448
00:37:53,580 --> 00:37:54,420
narealize ko ba

449
00:37:54,950 --> 00:37:56,580
na ang lahat ay bitag lang niya.

450
00:37:58,990 --> 00:37:59,830
Sa kasamaang palad,

451
00:38:00,950 --> 00:38:01,830
huli na ang lahat.

452
00:38:04,910 --> 00:38:05,950
Hindi ako naniwala

453
00:38:05,950 --> 00:38:06,990
namatay ang aking ama para sa pag-ibig.

454
00:38:08,020 --> 00:38:09,500
Ikaw ay mayabang at suwail,

455
00:38:10,830 --> 00:38:12,220
ngunit hindi ka kailanman nagsamantala.

456
00:38:13,270 --> 00:38:14,470
Kung pinatay mo ang aking ama,

457
00:38:15,310 --> 00:38:16,830
sana sinabi mo sa lahat.

458
00:38:17,790 --> 00:38:20,390
Hindi mo kailangan ang dahilan na iyon.

459
00:38:22,180 --> 00:38:23,140
Hindi ako makaget-over nito

460
00:38:23,660 --> 00:38:25,270
hanggang sa mahuli ko si Yan Ke.

461
00:38:28,390 --> 00:38:29,230
Mula sa araw na ito,

462
00:38:31,580 --> 00:38:32,910
tugisin ang taksil na si Yan Ke.

463
00:38:33,540 --> 00:38:34,870
I-restart ang curfew.

464
00:38:35,580 --> 00:38:36,540
Masusing mag-imbestiga

465
00:38:36,550 --> 00:38:38,100
lahat ng kaguluhan sa nakalipas na limang taon.

466
00:38:38,580 --> 00:38:39,910
Mahigpit na parusahan ang mga lumabag

467
00:38:41,180 --> 00:38:42,140
ang mga Dekretong Golden-wall.

468
00:38:43,990 --> 00:38:44,830
Oo.

469
00:38:48,990 --> 00:38:49,830
Ilipat!

470
00:38:52,660 --> 00:38:54,100
Opisyal, narinig ko...

471
00:38:54,100 --> 00:38:55,350
Tinapos ng kanyang Grace ang kanyang pag-iisa

472
00:38:55,350 --> 00:38:56,390
at sinimulan muli ang mga Dekreto.

473
00:38:56,390 --> 00:38:57,390
Totoo ba yan, officer?

474
00:38:59,580 --> 00:39:00,830
Mga order mula sa Her Grace!

475
00:39:01,540 --> 00:39:02,660
Mga kaguluhan sa nakalipas na limang taon

476
00:39:03,020 --> 00:39:04,180
iimbestigahan!

477
00:39:04,750 --> 00:39:06,100
- Magaling!
- Mahusay!

478
00:39:06,100 --> 00:39:06,940
Ilipat!

479
00:39:07,140 --> 00:39:07,980
Ito ay mahusay.

480
00:39:08,140 --> 00:39:09,060
Bumalik na ang kanyang Grace.

481
00:39:09,910 --> 00:39:11,430
Sa wakas ligtas na ako.

482
00:39:11,430 --> 00:39:12,270
Mahusay!

483
00:39:12,470 --> 00:39:13,910
Bumalik na ang kanyang Grace!

484
00:39:16,540 --> 00:39:17,580
Galing!

485
00:39:19,700 --> 00:39:21,910
Ang Left Token ay bumalik sa akin.

486
00:39:22,500 --> 00:39:23,910
Ang mga espiritung bato ay naging

487
00:39:23,910 --> 00:39:24,870
maayos na ipinamahagi.

488
00:39:26,540 --> 00:39:27,390
Limang taon na.

489
00:39:27,400 --> 00:39:28,700
I'm so happy to see you

490
00:39:28,990 --> 00:39:29,910
ligtas at maayos.

491
00:39:31,310 --> 00:39:32,150
Limang taon na.

492
00:39:32,580 --> 00:39:34,180
Napakasaya mo pa rin

493
00:39:34,310 --> 00:39:35,150
gaya ng dati.

494
00:39:35,540 --> 00:39:36,990
Kung gaano kita inggit.

495
00:39:37,750 --> 00:39:39,100
Ikaw na walang pananampalataya na taksil.

496
00:39:39,520 --> 00:39:40,390
Sa loob ng limang taon,

497
00:39:40,390 --> 00:39:41,470
nagtrabaho ka sa Yan Ke

498
00:39:41,470 --> 00:39:42,950
at namuhay ng medyo masagana!

499
00:39:43,100 --> 00:39:44,100
Paano ka pa nakarating?

500
00:39:49,100 --> 00:39:50,140
Sa ilalim ng utos ng Your Grace,

501
00:39:50,580 --> 00:39:52,390
Nag-undercover ako kay Yan Ke.

502
00:39:55,060 --> 00:39:56,020
Siya...

503
00:39:56,020 --> 00:39:57,910
Ito ang ebidensya ng paglabag

504
00:39:58,430 --> 00:40:00,310
ng ilang panginoon na nagpasakop kay Yan Ke.

505
00:40:01,310 --> 00:40:02,220
Mangyaring tingnan ang katotohanan.

506
00:40:03,140 --> 00:40:05,140
Kaya hindi ka naging loyal sa kanya,

507
00:40:05,620 --> 00:40:06,660
ngunit nagtrabaho bilang isang espiya?

508
00:40:07,500 --> 00:40:08,580
Syempre hindi ako naging loyal.

509
00:40:09,020 --> 00:40:10,020
Tiniis ko ang lahat ng mga taon na ito

510
00:40:11,140 --> 00:40:12,060
para lang sa araw na ito

511
00:40:12,220 --> 00:40:13,060
nang bumalik ang Her Grace

512
00:40:13,270 --> 00:40:14,110
at ayusin ang mga bagay.

513
00:40:16,180 --> 00:40:17,430
Nakakagulat yun, Yun.

514
00:40:17,580 --> 00:40:18,620
Napakaperpekto mong nagpanggap.

515
00:40:18,870 --> 00:40:20,380
For all these years, nagkamali ako ng judgement sayo.

516
00:40:20,580 --> 00:40:22,060
Halika na, magpupuyat ako sa iyo.

517
00:40:22,390 --> 00:40:23,350
Hoy, Leiqi.

518
00:40:23,350 --> 00:40:24,190
Hindi mahalaga.

519
00:40:26,830 --> 00:40:28,390
Lahat tayo ay nagtatrabaho para sa Kanyang Grasya.

520
00:40:36,430 --> 00:40:37,310
Baka bumangon ka.

521
00:40:39,340 --> 00:40:40,180
salamat po.

522
00:40:40,180 --> 00:40:41,020
Ito ay mahusay.

523
00:40:41,350 --> 00:40:42,540
Bumalik na ang kanyang Grace.

524
00:40:43,100 --> 00:40:44,910
Babalik sa normal ang Void.

525
00:40:45,720 --> 00:40:46,620
Kaya ganito

526
00:40:46,620 --> 00:40:47,620
may meeting sila ngayon.

527
00:40:48,540 --> 00:40:49,380
Interesting.

528
00:40:50,940 --> 00:40:54,940
(Liang)

529
00:40:55,310 --> 00:40:56,870
Ihatid ang intel kay Wu Shengliu.

530
00:41:25,710 --> 00:41:31,570
♪Ang mga naantig na alaala ay nananatili tulad ng mga anino♪

531
00:41:32,200 --> 00:41:37,710
♪Kalat-kalat na repleksyon
lumubog sa puso ko♪

532
00:41:38,300 --> 00:41:44,310
♪Kung pwede kitang tawaging ganito ng mahina♪

533
00:41:45,400 --> 00:41:50,010
♪Kasing banayad ng isang panandaliang yakap♪

534
00:41:52,140 --> 00:41:53,620
Limang taon na!

535
00:41:53,620 --> 00:41:54,830
Alam mo ba kung gaano siya nag-aalala?

536
00:41:54,830 --> 00:41:55,670
Ikaw...

537
00:41:57,780 --> 00:42:03,400
♪Ibinigay ang habambuhay
para maalala ang isang pangalan♪

538
00:42:03,930 --> 00:42:07,290
♪May mga hilig at sakit♪

539
00:42:07,490 --> 00:42:10,390
♪Sana maranasan natin silang magkasama♪

540
00:42:11,070 --> 00:42:17,300
♪Bago tayo makalimutan o maghiwalay♪

541
00:42:18,610 --> 00:42:21,370
♪Kahit na bumigay ang araw sa gabi♪

542
00:42:21,370 --> 00:42:23,020
♪ Lumalabo at kumukupas♪

543
00:42:23,020 --> 00:42:25,850
♪Ano kaya ang mangyayari?♪

544
00:42:26,260 --> 00:42:27,760
♪Wala akong pakialam kundi ikaw♪

545
00:42:27,760 --> 00:42:29,410
♪Lalapit ako at tatakbo sa iyo♪

546
00:42:29,410 --> 00:42:32,590
♪Upang pagalingin ang pinakamalalim na sugat♪

547
00:42:33,110 --> 00:42:35,800
♪Mga himala, kawalang-hanggan, at ningning♪

548
00:42:35,800 --> 00:42:38,550
♪Mas mahalaga kaysa sa anumang tigang na lupa♪

549
00:42:38,790 --> 00:42:41,150
♪Maaari din ako
gugulin ang natitirang bahagi ng aking buhay♪

550
00:42:41,150 --> 00:42:45,120
♪Paglalakad kasama ka sa kawalang-hanggan♪

551
00:42:57,620 --> 00:42:58,460
Simu,

552
00:42:59,500 --> 00:43:00,430
ikaw ba talaga yan

553
00:43:01,470 --> 00:43:02,500
Nandito ka ba talaga?

554
00:43:03,870 --> 00:43:04,710
Ako ito.

555
00:43:05,040 --> 00:43:09,890
♪Kahit magkahiwalay, umiikot pa rin ang iniisip ko♪

556
00:43:09,910 --> 00:43:11,390
Pinatawag kita ng maraming beses.

557
00:43:14,020 --> 00:43:14,860
alam ko.

558
00:43:18,220 --> 00:43:19,060
Pero hindi ka dumating.

559
00:43:22,100 --> 00:43:23,270
Ngayon, dumating na ako.

560
00:43:24,600 --> 00:43:29,700
♪Bago tayo makalimutan o maghiwalay♪

561
00:43:29,820 --> 00:43:31,680
♪Kahit na bumigay ang araw sa gabi♪

562
00:43:31,680 --> 00:43:33,290
♪ Lumalabo at kumukupas♪

563
00:43:33,290 --> 00:43:36,140
♪Ano kaya ang mangyayari?♪

564
00:43:36,660 --> 00:43:38,100
♪Wala akong pakialam kundi ikaw♪

565
00:43:38,100 --> 00:43:39,750
♪Lalapit ako at tatakbo sa iyo♪

566
00:43:39,750 --> 00:43:43,000
♪Upang pagalingin ang pinakamalalim na sugat♪

567
00:43:43,420 --> 00:43:46,030
♪Mga himala, kawalang-hanggan, at ningning♪

568
00:43:47,100 --> 00:43:47,940
ayos lang ako.

569
00:43:49,080 --> 00:43:51,490
♪Maaari din ako
gugulin ang natitirang bahagi ng aking buhay♪

570
00:43:51,490 --> 00:43:55,500
♪Paglalakad kasama ka sa kawalang-hanggan♪

571
00:44:00,180 --> 00:44:01,270
Hindi pa ako naging

572
00:44:01,270 --> 00:44:02,220
na hindi mapakali.

573
00:44:03,750 --> 00:44:04,870
Hindi kita naabot.

574
00:44:06,540 --> 00:44:08,310
At hindi ko alam kung ano ang nangyayari.

575
00:44:11,620 --> 00:44:12,460
Huwag kang mag-alala.

576
00:44:14,700 --> 00:44:16,180
Kung may nangyari sa akin,

577
00:44:17,220 --> 00:44:18,350
alam mo sana.

578
00:44:20,060 --> 00:44:21,750
Kung ako ay nalipol,

579
00:44:22,750 --> 00:44:24,430
ang mundo ay nahulog sa kaguluhan

580
00:44:25,540 --> 00:44:26,750
at ang mga sakuna ay magaganap.

581
00:44:41,440 --> 00:44:46,770
♪Sa pagitan ng itim at puti,
ripples crossed♪

582
00:44:47,100 --> 00:44:51,350
♪Light encountered shadow♪

583
00:44:52,710 --> 00:44:58,080
♪Natusok nito ang dilim at oras♪

584
00:44:58,380 --> 00:45:02,980
♪Ang hindi mababasag na kapalaran♪

585
00:45:04,070 --> 00:45:05,910
♪Biglang basag♪

586
00:45:18,120 --> 00:45:23,560
♪Sa pagitan ng itim at puti,
ripples crossed♪

587
00:45:23,740 --> 00:45:28,070
♪Light encountered shadow♪

588
00:45:29,440 --> 00:45:34,830
♪Natusok nito ang dilim at oras♪

589
00:45:35,060 --> 00:45:39,000
♪Ang hindi mababasag na kapalaran♪

590
00:45:40,770 --> 00:45:42,660
♪Biglang basag♪

591
00:45:45,320 --> 00:45:48,480
♪Makinig, umaatungal ang lahat ng tunog♪

592
00:45:48,480 --> 00:45:51,010
♪Habang ang malamig na yelo ay nagiging tides♪

593
00:45:51,010 --> 00:45:56,530
♪Ang kalungkutan ng isang siglo ay nakakatunaw ng mga pangarap♪

594
00:45:56,530 --> 00:45:59,770
♪Pagsunod sa patnubay ng tadhana♪

595
00:45:59,770 --> 00:46:04,630
♪Sa tadhana, ang ating mga sandali ay ipinagpalit♪

596
00:46:04,970 --> 00:46:07,990
♪Nagising ang puso bigla♪

597
00:46:07,990 --> 00:46:10,810
♪Panoorin ang pagbagsak ng mga paputok na parang bituin♪

598
00:46:11,070 --> 00:46:13,600
♪Ang bono na ito ay gusot sa isang thread♪

599
00:46:13,600 --> 00:46:19,020
♪Ang mga makamundong pagmuni-muni ay kumukupas sa ambon♪

600
00:46:19,190 --> 00:46:22,260
♪Pahiram ng isang panandaliang tibok ng puso♪

601
00:46:22,420 --> 00:46:27,320
♪Dinala mo ako sa mortal na alikabok,
hanggang sa nabighani ako sa mga alindog nito♪

602
00:46:27,530 --> 00:46:31,000
♪Ang puso ay nagising bigla♪

